No.55/4/CF-69
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
( Department of Cabinet Affairs)
IMMEDIATE
New Delhi, the 24th July, 1969
2nd Sravana, 1891.
The undersigned is directed to state that with
effect from the afternoon of July 19, 1969, Shri Morarji R. Desai
relinquished charge of his office as Minister for the Union.
aha
(R, N, Kalia)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Prime Minister/
the Joint Secretary to the Prime Minister/the Private Secretary
to the Prime Minister, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President,
for information.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/the Chairman,
Rail way Board/the Secretary, Planning Commission/the Secretary,
Department of Parliamentary Affairs/the Secretary, Election.
Commission/Chairman, Union Public Service Commission/Comptroll er
and Auditor General of India, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of Government
of India/the Lok Sabha Secretariat/the Rajya Sabha Secretariat,
for information.
aha
(R, N, Kalia)
Under Secretary to the Cabin et.
* JAISWAL *
